OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of strangling
OL,4,Cgirl, 16, while she was handcuffed
OL,6,FA Nottinghamshire Police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen cleared of strangling a 16-year-
OL,8,Fold girl who was in custody and
OL,9,Fhandcuffed inside a police vehicle.
OL,11,FPolice Constable (PC) Kevin Markowski,
OL,12,Faged 46, was found not guilty by a
OL,13,Fjury at Lincoln Crown Court, following
OL,14,Fa six-day trial.
OL,16,FMarkowski was charged with non-fatal,
OL,17,Fintentional strangulation of a child,
OL,18,Fan offence under section 75A(1)(a) and
OL,19,F(5) of the Serious Crime Act 2015,
OL,20,Ffollowing an alleged incident on 24
OL,21,FAugust 2022 in Arnold, Nottingham.
