OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of strangling
OL,4,Cgirl, 16, while she was handcuffed
OL,6,FThe police officer was investigated
OL,7,Ffor his use of force during the
OL,8,Fdetainment of the girl, who had been
OL,9,Finvolved in a verbal altercation with
OL,10,Fother young women in the street. She
OL,11,Fwas detained for breach of the peace,
OL,12,Fhandcuffed, and placed in the back of
OL,13,Fa police vehicle.
OL,15,FDuring the trial, body-worn video
OL,16,Ffootage was presented, showing PC
OL,17,FMarkowski with his hands on the girl's
OL,18,Fneck or chest area on two occasions.
