OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of strangling
OL,4,Cgirl, 16, while she was handcuffed
OL,6,FIOPC Regional Director David Ford
OL,7,Fsaid: "Given the seriousness of the
OL,8,Fallegation, it was right for the
OL,9,Fevidence to be tested in a public
OL,10,Fcourt. We respect the jury's decision
OL,11,Fand will now be liaising with the
OL,12,Fforce on the next steps."
OL,14,FDuring the investigation police
OL,15,Fanalysed the available BWV and CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage; interviewed the girl and the
OL,17,Ftwo officers involved; and obtained
OL,18,Fstatements from several witnesses.
