OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of strangling
OL,4,Cgirl, 16, while she was handcuffed
OL,6,FPC Markowski was cleared of
OL,7,Fstrangulation by a jury after five
OL,8,Fhours and 51 minutes of deliberations.
OL,9,FJudge James House KC thanked the jury
OL,10,Ffor their work before addressing
OL,11,FMarkowski.
OL,13,FHe said: "You have been acquitted by
OL,14,Fthe jury so I am formally discharging
OL,15,Fyou. You are free to go."
OL,17,FMr Markowski responded: "Thank you
OL,18,Fyour honour."
